      <title>中国建筑商远洋集团在伦敦寻求债务计划批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/chinese-builder-sino-ocean-seeks-debt-plan-approval-in-london</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的中国建筑商远洋集团控股有限公司将于周三在伦敦一家法院接受为期三天的听证会，寻求行使一项法律机制，允许债务人在未获得债权人完全批准的情况下完成重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/chinese-builder-sino-ocean-seeks-debt-plan-approval-in-london</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
